##########################
Torque Batch Script Usage:
##########################

pbsnodes
#Show information about use status of each node.

qstat -a
#Shows queue / jobs status (running, waiting, completed or canceled).

qstat -n
#Shows allocated nodes/cores.

qdel <job ID>
#Cancel a job (the job ID can be viewed from qstat).

qsub exemplos/Batchjob
#Submit a job in batch script mode.

"Batchjob" is the batch script file where job submission commands and parameters are specified. An example can be found in ~/exemplos/torque 
directory.
